<br>
Most of my time was spent in the market channel and in the auction zone on my server (this was pre-bazaar) clearing my bank of the things I had collected over the past 20 or so levels.<br>
<br>
I started with practically no cash in my bank.<br>
<br>
I had these items, many of which also drop in Crystal Caverns:<br>
<br>
Cane of the Tranquil, in my offhand when I used 1 hand combos. -- 500pp.<br>
Robe of Living Fungus, in my Chest slot.  Sold for 900pp and equipped a Crystal Covered Shroud I had in the bank.<br>
Blackened Crystalline Robe, in my bank -- 300pp<br>
Blackened Crystalline Robe, on a mule (I had been in CC for a while) - 300pp<br>
Crystal Covered Shroud, on a mule -- 200pp<br>
Crystal Covered Shroud, on a second mule -- 200pp<br>
Crystal Covered Shroud, in my chest slot -- 200pp<br>
Light Velium Brawl Stick, in my primary slot (I liked it better than Jade Mace/Cane of the Tranquil) -- 3000pp to a friend (Yeah I ripped him off)<br>
About 20 Orc Fang Earrings sold at 20pp each -- 400pp<br>
5 Ry`Gorr pieces at 200p each -- 1000pp<br>
<br>
I sold this last, as my hand to hand wasn't very high, and I needed to have good Damage Per Second:<br>
Jade Mace -- 4000pp<br>
<br>
And then I bought Imbued Fighters Staff for 11,000pp and my friends were SO envious.<br>
<br>
I assume Fungus Covered Scale Tunic would be about the same list, only 5 times longer.<br>
<br>
It is possible, but it will take time .. time you must be willing to put exp on hold for. <p>-Korph
<br>
